          "reviewBody": "“Fantastic school! The teachers are Professional, caring and well organized. Being a teacher as well as a parent i am satisfied with the education qualities provided to the children. May be this is the only school where one to one teaching is provided to the students for senior classes also. Children are looking forward to coming to school as they get the opportunity to participate in a variety of activities and events throughout the year. The school is having a huge playground,  swimming pool, basketball and badminton court. The school is also running an after -school sports academy within the school premises for kids after school hours.",
          "publisher": {
